<h3>Hello,</h3>
<p>Thank you for buying locally through KFOM! The following is a summary of your orders for the week.All orders must be picked up this <strong>Thursday between 5-7 pm at the Herald & News Building</strong> (2701 Foothills Blvd, follow signs to side entrance). Cash, check, and SNAP are all accepted forms of payment and <u>each producer must be paid separately</u>. If you choose to pay with cash, please separate exact change into envelopes for each producer.</p>
<br />
<p>Only producers whose minimum total was met will fulfill orders, which are listed below.</p>
<br />
  <table style='width:100%;'>
    <thead>
      <th>Producer Name</th>
      <th>Contact Info</th>
      <th>Order Details</th>
      <th>Check Payable To</th>
      <th>Total</th>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <% @order_items.each do |seller, items| %>
      <% subtotal = 0 %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= seller.profile.business_name %></td>
        <td>
          <li><%= seller.email %></li>
          <li><%= seller.profile.phone_formatted %></li>
        </td>
        <td>
          <% items.each do |i| %>
            <% subtotal = subtotal.to_f + (i.quantity.to_i * i.post.price.to_f) %>
            <li><%= "#{i.post.title} - Quantity to pick up: #{i.quantity}"  %> </li>
          <% end %>
        </td>
        <td><%= seller.profile.payable_to %></td>
        <td><%= number_to_currency(subtotal) %></td>
      </tr>
      <% end %>
    </tbody>
  </table>
<br />
<em>Please read the instructions below. Detailed policies & procedures can be found in your welcome email you received when you registered.</em>
