<h4>Payment:</h4>
<p>If you would like to pay using your SNAP benefits, please bring your Oregon Trail card to pay at pickup.  Please be prepared to pay any remaining balance with cash or check.</p>

<p><strong>Customers who fail to pick up are still responsible to pay the producer.</strong> Failure to pay will result in cancellation of your membership with KFOM. Alternative pickup times will <u>not</u> be arranged.</p>

<h4>Questions?</h4>

<p>Please contact food producers directly with any questions regarding your order. Other questions can be directed to KFOM.</p>

